      <title>西塔拉曼称印度近期经济增长乏力只是暂时现象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/india-s-recent-weak-growth-a-temporary-blip-sitharaman-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度财政部长尼尔玛拉·西塔拉曼称，印度上个季度经济扩张放缓只是“暂时现象”，并预计未来几个月经济将回升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/india-s-recent-weak-growth-a-temporary-blip-sitharaman-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 13:10:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西雷亚尔下跌，不受央行最新美元抛售影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/brazil-central-bank-steps-in-currency-markets-again-amid-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管巴西央行决策者承诺将利率上调至八年来的最高水平，但巴西央行周二在不到一周的时间内第三次在现货市场上抛售美元，试图将雷亚尔从历史低位拉升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/brazil-central-bank-steps-in-currency-markets-again-amid-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 12:45:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西央行称创纪录低汇率加剧通胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/brazil-s-central-bank-warns-price-outlook-worsened-significantly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西央行表示，由于货币贬值和需求强劲等因素，通胀风险正在成为现实，这迫使央行董事会一致表示，到 3 月份借贷成本将上升至 14% 以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/brazil-s-central-bank-warns-price-outlook-worsened-significantly</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 11:45:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
